Let us begone, cried the surgeon, in evident
agitation
.
What ails you?
I have been for years endeavouring to discover the
means of prolonging life, and imagined that I had
perfected
my theory. But in the presence of such a
commentary
upon its futility, the mighty fabric falls to the
