Miriam Grey.
She here? Good heavens! When did she come?
A few hours ago.
Poor misguided girl!
Fatally misguided, indeed.
Wherefore is she from her home? What does she
here?
She asks for shelter for the night. You best can
answer why she has deserted her mother's roof.
